casebody.data:
Graham, Appellant, v. Merritt, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. December 23, 1891.) Appeal from ninth district court. Action by David S. Graham against Robert B. Merritt.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bisohoff, JJ.

L. M. Knowles, for appellant. A. McDonald, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
